Hardware Connections
DS3231 RTC Module:

SDA -> GPIO21 (default SDA on ESP32)
SCL -> GPIO22 (default SCL on ESP32)
VCC -> 3.3V
GND -> GND
DHT22 Sensor:

Data Pin -> GPIO15 (can be any GPIO)
VCC -> 3.3V
GND -> GND
16x2 LCD with I2C Interface:

SDA -> GPIO21 (same SDA line as RTC)
SCL -> GPIO22 (same SCL line as RTC)
VCC -> 3.3V
GND -> GND
Libraries Required
1.RTClib for the DS3231 module
2.DHT sensor library for the DHT22 sensor
3.LiquidCrystal_I2C for the 16x2 I2C LCD display

You can install these libraries from the Arduino Library Manager.
